text.tspan: Ulferen Longtooth Shifter | Eldritch Knight Fighter 4
DARKVISION: Dim -> bright w/i 60' & dark -> dim
HEART: Commoners try to help me & will fight
w/me if I'm alone, unless I'm a danger to them
THIEVES' CANT: 4x longer but can hide messages
CAT'S BURST: 1 turn w/2x speed, move 0' to regain
ASSASSINATE: Adv on attack vs target that hasn't
had a turn yet. Hit on Surprised ---> Critical
SNEAK ATTACK: if hit w/finesse or range weapon
AND (have Adv w/attack OR target w/i 5' of
Appearance: Born during eclipse; has darker fur;
Radiant followers believe it a bad omen
Easily distracted, forgets lessons. Compulsive if
Self-interested: items - or people - are disposable
once exhausted of new info. Not honor-bound.
Distrusts divine beings; guarded around clerics.
- The Radiant religious sect & Risers group
- Tabaxi tavern bard from northern road
- Clear a mine for the Rustbeards?
- Resolution of moral code; develop patience?
Artifacts: an obsidian one, and a green marble-y one
Misc: backpack, BBs, bedroll, bell, candle, crowbar, dragon tooth,
hammer, hooded lantern, mess kit, necklace, oil, pitons, 10d rations,
ring, string, tinderbox, torches, waterskin, thief tools*
OppAttack - melee attack if enemy I see moves out of reach
C - MAGIC STONE (BA, 1m, 60'): Turn <=3 pepples into magic range weapons - 1d6+5
C - PRIMAL SAVAGERY (A, 5'): Melee spell attack - 2d10 acid
1 - ABSORB ELEMENT (R): Resist acid/cold/fire/lightning/thunder & +1d6 next melee
1 - ENTANGLEC (A, 1m, 90'): Difficult terrain in 20' sq. STR save or Restrained
2 - HEAT METALC (A, 1m, 60'): A metal obj - 2d8 fire + (CON & drops) or DisAdv
Add animal glyphs of the castes
